<HEADLINE> Smirnov Wins Men's 30km Cross Country in World Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HELSINKI, January 19 (Xinhua) -- Vladimir Smirnov of Kazahkstan
clocked one hour, 15 minutes and 28 seconds to win the men's
