<TEXT>
<P>
CHANGSHA, January 20 (Xinhua) -- The provincial government of
China's Hunan Province today announced the dismissal of three
officials who were accused of incompetence, and the public
criticism of two others, all of whom held senior posts as
department directors in the provincial government.
</P>
