Austria beat American 11th seed Jim Courier in four sets to reach
the Australian Open quarter-finals in Melbourne on Monday.
</P>
<P>
Muster overcame injuries on his shoulder and feet during his
6-2 3-6 7-6 6-3 victory in a match lasting two hours 42 minutes
which ended in the early hours of Tuesday.
