have done geographical studies of the region and have engaged in
manoeuvres to improve their skill.
</P>
<P>
The air force units are making progress in preparation for
being stationed in the SAR.
</P>
<P>
The Central Military Commission and some other units inspected
237 companies last November, and found 97 percent of the troops to
be of excellent caliber, Major General Liu said. 
