Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
Li assured the 85-member group, led by Yoshio Sakuauchi,
president of the Japanese Association for the Promotion of
International Trade, that the policies of "one country, two
systems", and "Hong Kong people governing Hong Kong", with a high
degree of autonomy will finally be realized.
</P>
