cooperation has continued to increase over the past several years,
and even though political relations are not satisfactory, the
meeting between Prime Minister Hashimoto and President Jiang Zemin
last year during the APEC meeting proved to be a turning point in
bilateral ties, which is gratifying.
</P>
<P>
He called for new cooperative relations based on mutual trust,
to help Japan-China relations.
</P>
<P>
