<HEADLINE> Romanian Runner Tests Positive for Doping </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, January 20 (Xinhua) -- European women's cross
country champion Iulia Negura tested positive for a banned
substance in a test carried out by the International Amateur
Athletic Federation, Romania's athletics body said on Monday.
</P>
<P>
