<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, January 19 (Xinhua) -- Mexico took revenge as they
beat hosts the United States 2-0 in the U.S. Cup soccer tournament
at Pasadena on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The Mexican team took the game through Luis Roberto Alves and
