<HEADLINE> Improved Mainland-HK Economic Ties to Boost Businessmen's Confidence In Future (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
With a favorable investment environment, and the vast inland
areas as its backyard, Hong Kong will continue to be one of the
most competitive regions in the world after July 1 this year, he
said.
</P>
<P>
The world business community is generally confident in Hong
Kong's investment and trade prospects, viewing Hong Kong's return
as a promise of more investment opportunities.
</P>
<P>
According to recent statistics published by the Hong Kong
government, nearly 40 percent of the 4,500 foreign-invested
companies in Hong Kong established their commercial presence in
the past five years, he said.
</P>
<P>
