<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, January 20 (Xinhua) -- Iran's Foreign Ministry
protested against Pakistan over the burning of Iranian facilities
in Lahore by summoning Pakistani ambassador late Sunday night,
local media reported today.
</P>
