Pakistani government to bring to justice those responsible for
this anti-Iran act.
</P>
<P>
Observers here noted that the incident would affect the
relations between Iran and Pakistan, which have already been
cool due to their competition in the Afghan issue.
</P>
<P>
The official report said that members of the Sipah Sahaba
Pakistan (SSP) attacked the center's library in Lahore Sunday,
setting fire to thousands of books, including copies of the
Koran.
</P>
