<TEXT>
<P>
MOGADISHU, January 20 (Xinhua) -- Somali faction leader Ali
Mahdi Mohamed, at a press conference yesterday, called on the
Somalis to refrain from violence and armed conflicts, but
practice maximum restraint at this crucial moment.
</P>
