<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, January 20 (Xinhua) -- American 14th seed Mary Joe
Fernandez clinched her quarter-final berth after battling her way
through three-set to win Patty Schnyder of Switzerland in the
Australia Open in Melbourne.
</P>
