communications as well as economic cooperation between Myanmar and
the Chinese province, which will help promote economic growth and
social development in the country, the report said.
</P>
<P>
The completed section, measuring 44.8 kilometers and
inaugurated last Saturday, was constructed by a Myanmar private
company -- the Asia World Co. Ltd. under a contract reached last
July with the Myanmar Ministry of Construction.  
