<HEADLINE> Good Service From South Chinese Corporation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, January 20 (Xinhua) -- Guangdong Province's Foreign
Enterprise Service Corporation (FESCO) has for its motto "If you
meet with difficulties, please come see me."
</P>
<P>
FESCO supplies various services for foreign-backed enterprises
and permanent representative offices of foreign companies in this
southern Chinese province.
</P>
<P>
In 1996, it handled 114 requests from foreign companies to set
up their representative offices in Guangdong, and did industrial
and commercial registration work for 80 foreign enterprises, and
provided nearly 1,000 people for foreign organizations.
</P>
<P>
FESCO also supplied insurance services, tax advice, and visa
services. It has relations with over 400 foreign organizations.
</P>
